## Limitations

The report is based on available data and articles up to October 2023, and some sources may not reflect the most current developments in energy pricing. Additionally, the analysis is limited to the information provided by the selected articles, which may not cover all possible factors influencing energy prices. Further research could provide a more comprehensive understanding of the issue.